{"tid":383042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川9歲女蹲盲眼位玩耍　遭父駕車輾斃","createTime":"2017-09-01T07:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T11:07:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bde19d77ab685021a556340795222e5e740182d9","tid":383042,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/153138_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F153138_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=a93defd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170901/photo/bkncn-20170901080259246-0901_05011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170901%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170901080259246-0901_05011_001_01p.jpg&h=cb1dc00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">蹲地玩耍的女童（紅圈示）遭其父駕駛的房車輾壓而過，浴血當場倒仰地上。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n四川都江堰周三（8月30日）發生一宗致命車禍，一名9歲女童慘遭一輛私家車輾壓，送抵醫院搶救前已經氣絕身亡。而更令人痛心的是，肇事司機正是被輾斃女童的父親。<br />\n<br />\n周三下午2時許，肇事司機當時駕車帶着9歲女兒及母親到一座液化氣站入氣。隨後，肇事司機上車駛離前，喊了女兒一聲讓其上車，惟女童未有理會並繼續蹲地玩耍。<br />\n<br />\n從液化氣站閉路電視畫面所見，由於未有察覺女兒沒有登車，加上女童疑置身在「盲眼位」，導致肇事司機駕車直接將女兒輾壓而過。女童被輾過後，渾身是血倒臥現場，其祖母在旁哭泣大叫「孫女兒啊」，而肇事司機則捂臉痛不欲生。最終女童被上救護車後，來不及送抵醫院搶救已傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170901/bkncn-20170901080259246-0901_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170901%2Fbkncn-20170901080259246-0901_05011_001.html&d=7YrFDRuc1Y%2FoZZeHiVOtiI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5ed49aee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170901/bkncn-20170901080259246-0901_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47bda8777c5897cf7807d773189a4e822e430d0f","tid":383042,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767a204ca37a45d8531982a97b14b805606e8082","tid":383042,"uid":38523,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:36:53.000Z","msg":"前面咁多位係要後退？<br />\n再睇<br />\n原來係女<br />\n明晒"},{"pid":"e5310101762c700d70c3f85fa099803f37c925d9","tid":383042,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估你唔到1"},{"pid":"e0c7d770faeeb85f29f23426a4ecbf155e1bd63c","tid":383042,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"離正係轆後面，好陰人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304376c03ab1795b7daedbb4b159ddbcc04ceb96","tid":383042,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前面咁多位係要後退？<br />\n再睇<br />\n原來係女<br />\n明晒</blockquote><br />\n可以追仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd93daa9d0cca5cd61a5dd75c6ff90f218d3ee","tid":383042,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前面咁多位係要後退？<br />\n再睇<br />\n原來係女<br />\n明晒</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁話 個場咁撚大 咁玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4714d390824abc63d89d33f98b1028b862c74983","tid":383042,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"中國人命運"},{"pid":"e5d766cb9206997289957205a55bff7f20f5b674","tid":383042,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:00:34.000Z","msg":"叻哥.jpg"},{"pid":"6baea12ac6bcc6e9f218dd296279cc2972fe5103","tid":383042,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquot